  """
  This function checks if two words are anagrams of each other.

  Args:
    word1: The first word.
    word2: The second word.

  Returns:
    "Anagrams!" if the words are anagrams, 
    "Dress-up!" if they are not anagrams but look similar,
    "Nope!" if they are not anagrams.
